Subject: drm/i915: Use a plain old int for the cdclk/mdclk ratio
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 96c420d5016e5bec57dccb161744c43366b72eca
